snippet.title: DARWAKE: Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Darwake Demo Out Now On Steam! Play it and share it with your friends:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2184850/Darwake_Awakening_from_the_Nightmare/

A 2D puzzle adventure set in a dark eerie world. Our melancholic hero Darwin, accompanied by a mysterious Owl, must find a way out of a maze by solving environmental puzzles and fighting embodied nightmares.

#horror #games #steam #indie #Darwake
